<%- layout("layouts/boilerplate") %>

<div class="aircover-hosts-page">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="hero-section">
      <h1>AirCover for Hosts</h1>
      <p class="lead">Top-to-bottom protection for your home</p>
      <p>Host with confidence knowing you're protected with $1M damage protection, liability insurance, and more.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-8">
        <h2>What's included in AirCover for Hosts</h2>
        
        <div class="protection-features">
          <div class="feature-card">
            <h3><i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i> $1M damage protection</h3>
            <p>Your home is protected against damages caused by guests, up to $1 million.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <h3><i class="fas fa-home"></i> Host liability insurance</h3>
            <p>You're covered if you're found legally responsible for a guest getting hurt.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <h3><i class="fas fa-clipboard-check"></i> AirCover for stays</h3>
            <p>Guests get protection too, which helps them book with confidence.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <h3><i class="fas fa-building"></i> Damage protection for experiences</h3>
            <p>Protection for spaces used during experiences and activities.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2>How AirCover protects you</h2>
        <div class="protection-steps">
          <div class="step-card">
            <div class="step-number">1</div>
            <h3>Report the damage</h3>
            <p>If a guest causes damage, report it within 14 days of checkout.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="step-card">
            <div class="step-number">2</div>
            <h3>We review your claim</h3>
            <p>Our team reviews your claim and may request documentation.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="step-card">
            <div class="step-number">3</div>
            <h3>We resolve the issue</h3>
            <p>We'll pay for repairs or reimburse you for covered damages.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2>What's covered</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Accidental damage to your home and belongings</li>
          <li>Theft by a guest</li>
          <li>Deep cleaning required due to exceptional mess</li>
          <li>Income loss if your home becomes uninhabitable</li>
          <li>Liability for bodily injury to guests</li>
          <li>Damage to common areas in shared buildings</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>What's not covered</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Normal wear and tear</li>
          <li>Damage caused by you or your pets</li>
          <li>Damage caused by someone you invited</li>
          <li>Lost income due to your own cancellations</li>
          <li>Cash, securities, and other high-value items</li>
          <li>Intentional damage by the host</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Exclusions and limitations</h2>
        <p>AirCover for Hosts has certain exclusions and limitations. Please review the full policy details for complete information.</p>
        <a href="#" class="btn-link">View full policy details →</a>

        <h2>Frequently asked questions</h2>
        <div class="faq-section">
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>Do I need to pay extra for AirCover?</h3>
            <p>No, AirCover for Hosts is included automatically at no extra cost when you host on Wanderlust.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>How do I file a claim?</h3>
            <p>You can file a claim through your host account or by contacting our support team.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>What documentation do I need?</h3>
            <p>You may need photos of the damage, receipts for repairs, and a police report for theft.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>How long does it take to process a claim?</h3>
            <p>Most claims are processed within 10 business days, though complex cases may take longer.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="sidebar-card">
          <h3>Quick links</h3>
          <ul class="sidebar-links">
            <li><a href="/aircover">AirCover for guests</a></li>
            <li><a href="/hosting-resources">Hosting resources</a></li>
            <li><a href="/helpcenter">Help Center</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="sidebar-card mt-4">
          <h3>Need to file a claim?</h3>
          <p>Contact our support team to start the claims process.</p>
          <a href="/helpcenter" class="btn btn-primary btn-block">File a claim</a>
        </div>

        <div class="sidebar-card mt-4">
          <h3>Not a host yet?</h3>
          <p>Start hosting and get AirCover protection automatically.</p>
          <a href="/host-your-home" class="btn btn-outline-primary btn-block">Become a host</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
